cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.MM, cs.NE 

This paper focuses on medical image segmentation using deep learning and active learning techniques. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The paper also proposes a penalization scheme and a sample querying scheme, which are related to optimization and decision-making, respectively. Therefore, the paper may also belong to cs.LG (Machine Learning), cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence), and cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing). Finally, the paper deals with medical imaging, which is a subfield of multimedia (cs.MM).
